Name: Rockochet
About the game: Rockochet is a VR Arcade-style game with two very simple mechanics: move and bounce. Your player's shield launches an energy ball that knocks ore stones from the large space rock. Keep the ball in play by orbiting around and bouncing it back towards the rock. Capture ore stones with your shield for points and upgrades.
